  <section>
    <title>Welcome to Callimachus</title>
    <para>If you're seeing this page via a web browser, it means you've installed Callimachus successfully. Congratulations!</para>
    <para>Using the username and password entered during the installation wizard, login using the button at the top.</para>
    <para>As you may have guessed by now, this is the default Callimachus home page. It can be change using the edit tab above once you are logged in.</para>
    <para>If you're seeing this page, and you don't think you should be, then you're either a user who has arrived at new installation of Callimachus, or you're an administrator who hasn't got his/her setup quite right. Providing the latter is the case, please refer to the <ulink url="http://callimachusproject.org/">Callimachus Website</ulink> or the README.txt file provided in the install directory.</para>
    <para>You can download sample applications following the <ulink url="http://code.google.com/p/callimachus/wiki/GettingStarted">Getting Started page</ulink>.</para>
    <para>Callimachus mailing lists are available at the <ulink url="http://callimachusproject.org/">Callimachus Website</ulink>.</para>
    <para>Thanks for using Callimachus!</para>
